OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWarm for central and eastern
OL,6,Fareas with some very warm. Southeast
OL,7,Fwinds fresh around the coasts, pegging
OL,8,Fback temperatures around the east
OL,9,Fcoast. Staying dry during the morning,
OL,10,Fthen patchy rain extending from the
OL,11,Fwest for the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with some patchy light
OL,14,Frain about, most of this during the
OL,15,Fevening and from Lough Neagh
OL,16,Fwestwards. Southerly winds easing
OL,17,Flight overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
