OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FTemperatures down from
OL,6,FTuesday. A rather cloudy morning with
OL,7,Fsome patchy rain, then most dry for
OL,8,Fthe afternoon with brighter spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,12,Fearly Thursday, clearing to showers
OL,13,Ffor the afternoon. Friday turning wet
OL,14,Fand windy with best of shelter in
OL,15,Feast. Showers Saturday, more frequent
OL,16,Fin west.
